  And I should see 'new-activity-count {&quot;count&quot;:4,&quot;num&quot;:4}' in mail
  And I open mail to "admin@test.com"
  And I should see '<b>hello-username {&quot;{username}&quot;:&quot;admin&quot;}</b><br>' in mail

